title: Lachhindeviki Oka Lekkundi ausio launch on October 11
text: 'Andala Rakshashi' pair Naveen Chandra and Lavanya Tripathi teamed up for a film titled Lachhindeviki Oka Lekkundi (LOL). The shooting was completed a couple of months ago and the post production work has been wrapped up recently. Jagadish Talasila, who worked as an assistant to SS Rajamouli, is the director for the film. As per the latest update, the film's audio launch will take place on October 11th at Shilpakala Vedika in Hyderabad. The music was composed by music maestro MM Keeravani. Sai Prasad Kamineni has produced the film. The release date will be announced very soon.
